  &lt;p id="uO5mF5"&gt;The holiday shopping season is here — which means it’s a great time to snag deals on smartwatches and fitness trackers. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="c-float-left c-float-hang"&gt;&lt;aside id="tBokZw"&gt;&lt;div data-anthem-component="readmore" data-anthem-component-data='{"stories":[{"title":"The best Black Friday tech&amp;amp;nbsp;deals&amp;amp;nbsp;we’ve found (so far)","url":"https://www.theverge.com/24307545/black-friday-2024-best-deals-tech-gadgets-cyber-monday-gift-ideas"},{"title":"How to choose which Apple Watch to buy","url":"https://www.theverge.com/23037217/best-apple-watch-series-se-ultra"},{"title":"The best smartwatches for Android","url":"https://www.theverge.com/23449363/best-android-smartwatches-wear-os"}]}'&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/aside&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
